     <div class="section"> 
      <h2 class="about">What We Do</h2> 
      <div class="content"> 
       <p> Scholarship America's mission is to mobilize America, through scholarships and educational support, to make postsecondary success possible for all students. We do this through core programs and businesses that support students in their education journey.<br> <br> <a href="dfs.php">Dollars for Scholars</a><br> <a href="dream_award.php">Dream Award</a><br> <a href="dk.php">Dreamkeepers</a><br> <a href="sms.php">Scholarship Management Services</a><br> <a href="http://familiesoffreedom.org" target="_blank">Families of Freedom Scholarship Fund </a></p> 
       <span class="more"><a href="about.php">Learn More</a></span> 
      </div>
